The '''Leagues Reward Shop''' is a store run by the [[League Tutor (Shattered Relics League)|League Tutor]] in [[Catherby]], near the [[bank]]. They sell rewards from [[Old School RuneScape Leagues]] in exchange for points earned within the Leagues on [[members]]' worlds.

